Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.30,0:00:12.15,OP,,0,0,0,,在心灵的街道中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.67,0:00:18.50,OP,,0,0,0,,闪耀着希望之光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:24.70,OP,,0,0,0,,用虚幻的羽翼挥动着梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:30.95,OP,,0,0,0,,是你与我寻找的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.27,0:00:47.47,OP,,0,0,0,,真理总是隐藏在眼中 蓝蓝的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:54.32,OP,,0,0,0,,我们要往何处去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:01:01.12,OP,,0,0,0,,俩人未来与现今的流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.42,0:01:06.75,OP,,0,0,0,,我们继续踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.80,0:01:13.62,OP,,0,0,0,,永远的目标地 无止尽的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.97,0:01:24.62,OP,,0,0,0,,希望能不放手不断追寻 直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.17,0:01:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落是我们的宿敌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借由搜集四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.88,0:01:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量变得越来越大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实他不只跟犬夜叉有仇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.35,0:01:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管任何时候\N他都不会自己动手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是卑劣的利用其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.16,0:01:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了解开\N弥勒法师所中的风穴咒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.16,0:01:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了救出珊瑚的弟弟\N被奈落囚禁的琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定要尽快的找到奈落\N打败他才行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.44,0:02:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第80话 杀生丸和被掳的小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.45,0:02:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么啦  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我闻到那家伙的臭味了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.75,0:02:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奈落没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风的味道变得不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.91,0:03:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小玲被人给掳走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚奈落的分身\N神乐突然出现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把小玲给抓走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管放一百万个心吧\N杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你肯乖乖听我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证那个叫小玲的\N一定会平安的回到你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落  又是你这个大坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么?这次又想要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.84,0:03:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实也没有特别想要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你肯帮我干掉犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就为了这么点小事\N需要这么大费周章吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.43,0:04:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为我杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会为了区区一个人类小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便乖乖地听命于你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道就这么放弃小玲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷  你要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你究竟要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终究还是跟来了  杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的\N闻到了奈落的味道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧  错不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落这个坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次让我抓到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非砍死他不可
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落一直神神秘秘\N从没有现身过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么突然会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.91,0:05:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要小心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被那个\N叫神乐的女人抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:05:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以  你不可以出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下你明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.35,0:06:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一出去\N马上会被他们撕成碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说\N你也是被他们抓回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样我们一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是负责看住你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  你叫什么名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你多大啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你是妖怪的同伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢吃什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西瓜喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个人话怎么这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.69,0:07:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都不说话好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷\N到底会不会来救我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底有什么打算嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.92,0:07:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问你到底有什么打算
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:07:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是奈落城
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里根本就不像是一座城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结界打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.74,0:08:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道奈落故意用臭味引诱我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我知道奈落城的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.18,0:08:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引我杀生丸进到里面去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:08:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不用一点小手段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你会不会\N乖乖自投罗网呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要找的小姑娘\N我不可能会把她藏在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座城堡到处都是瘴气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看不需要一分钟\N小姑娘就没气了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位小姑娘\N我暂时把她安置在城外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你们可以不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落  你这个坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是专程来救小玲的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一点至少你应该明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.35,0:09:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你杀生丸少爷\N一向都讨厌被人指挥的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是你所说的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你既不会去杀犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会特地来救小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那显然是来杀我奈落了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点我也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千方百计把我引来\N还在那里说风凉话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这笔帐待会再慢慢跟你算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:09:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还得看你有没有命活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.01,0:10:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不喜欢也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就让我陪你玩一玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.56,0:10:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.89,0:10:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我们大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总觉得\N四魂之玉碎片就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在对面那座山上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉碎片就在那座山上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.41,0:10:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.48,0:10:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们负责追踪四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.69,0:10:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搜奈落城的工作就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.69,0:10:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心一点  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的臭味突然之间消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道\N奈落城的结界又封闭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不快点又要找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是结界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去你的结界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:18.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的  风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤居然没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.11,0:11:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次你休想跑掉  大坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一路上真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:12:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就让我奈落\N好好的陪你玩个够
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是一些没用的死妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道这就是你的原形吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.79,0:12:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的原形
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对  这是小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才正要开始玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的想要\N我杀生丸这条命是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对奈落到底有什么好处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧  难道奈落这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉碎片就在这附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于被你感应到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.57,0:13:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说\N应该就在奈落城旁边了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想碎片应该是一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是珊瑚的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀身体里面刚好有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道真的是琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西瓜真的好甜喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还要不要再吃一片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我随时都可以再去偷一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.79,0:14:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀你真的什么都不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连自己的爸妈也不记得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我全忘光了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道连自己的父母都会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.70,0:14:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是完全没印象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候\N我会想起一些可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些事\N是你自己不愿意去回想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸爸妈妈还有我哥哥他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.22,0:14:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全家人都被强盗杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:42.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到现在还常常梦到他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得好难过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很吵对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.96,0:14:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都没出声  是不是觉得我很烦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.94,0:14:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经好久\N没有跟人说这么多话了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.39,0:15:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别出声
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人的样子我一直都记得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从来都没有忘掉过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.16,0:15:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子已经完全不记得\N自己做过些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.79,0:15:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经彻底毁在我的手里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今以后他什么都不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他死其实对他是一种解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  你在里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.15,0:16:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个下流的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒要看看你有什么能耐\N碰我杀生丸一根指头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒要仔细瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样的滥招数\N能玩到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉下来的这一片片肉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都会变成我身上的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落正在吸收杀生丸的肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让它变成自己身体的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.59,0:18:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会突然在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.13,0:18:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然在这里消失了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说这里是奈落城
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.17,0:18:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股毒气跟瘴气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.11,0:18:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是奈落的结界了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.60,0:18:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了  终于看到奈落城了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底什么人\N在城外破坏我的结界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐  马上去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有贵客到了  奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个客人也真倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大老远专程来拜访你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.86,0:19:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果\N他恐怕没机会见到你活着了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.93,0:19:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.94,0:19:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就大功告成了  臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻就会被我这块肉消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候\N你会变成我身体的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.95,0:19:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙的刀锋变成红色了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你破坏结界的是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还需要问吗  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子\N你已经不够资格跟我较量了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:19:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我劝你快点滚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站在那里  小心被我给砍死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你千万别跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.49,0:20:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要让你尝尝我的厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.99,0:20:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我跟你\N得好好打一场才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.27,0:20:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐之风一点杀气都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想不想打
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.47,0:20:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么一点都使不上劲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎被他看穿我毫无斗志了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来只好先在这挡一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:20:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就交给他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是一些笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.31,0:21:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的  风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.37,0:21:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸那小子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.61,0:21:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我太高估他了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.45,0:21:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.82,0:21:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.85,0:21:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚开  你们这帮妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.83,0:21:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以现在的犬夜叉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.89,0:21:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该可以打败奈落才对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.90,0:22:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要真是这样\N我就可以重获自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:37.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.75,0:22:21.35,ED,,0,0,0,,究竟要流多少泪{\fad(500,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:28.20,ED,,0,0,0,,Every Heart 才能坦白面对自己呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.82,0:22:35.02,ED,,0,0,0,,倘若对谁传达情感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.55,0:22:42.02,ED,,0,0,0,,Every Heart 是否就能得到满足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.02,0:22:48.32,ED,,0,0,0,,害怕着漫长漫长的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.47,0:22:55.40,ED,,0,0,0,,朝着遥远的星星祈祷着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:23:02.15,ED,,0,0,0,,在不停流转的时空之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.75,0:23:08.77,ED,,0,0,0,,我们都在寻找真正的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.25,0:23:15.82,ED,,0,0,0,,希望自己能够变得更坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.97,0:23:22.50,ED,,0,0,0,,今天也要抬头看着高高的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.80,0:23:29.12,ED,,0,0,0,,在不停流转的时空之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.60,0:23:35.75,ED,,0,0,0,,我们都在寻找生命的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.65,0:23:39.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.23,0:23:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是我失算
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.60,0:23:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到犬夜叉\N会采取这样的攻势
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.77,0:23:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落  等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.11,0:23:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我非打败你不可
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.87,0:23:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.01,0:23:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我奈落已经完全得到\N杀生丸身上的妖力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.95,0:24:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为\N那么容易可以打败我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.55,0:24:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说…杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.82,0:24:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不清楚你有多少能耐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.02,0:24:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你同样\N要成为我肉体的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.79,0:24:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.32,0:24:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落大坏蛋下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.26,0:24:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  马上给我杀了小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.40,0:24:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉宝典
